data.description: Affordable Mountain Home on 5.3 Acres with year-round access is a must see! Open floor plan provides lots of options. Large living room opens to breakfast area and kitchen. This home features a split floor plan with a large primary bedroom with large walk-in closet & private bath. Private bath includes double sink, soaker tub, and separate shower. The other end of the house features 3 additional bedrooms (all with large closets), a full bath with a tub/shower combo, and laundry room. Private patio in the back is great for entertaining. Fenced area in the front and along one side of the property. Located just 16 miles from the little mountain town of Westcliffe where groceries, specialty shops, health clinic and several restaurants are located. Westcliffe is the home of Dark Skies, Bluegrass Festival, and a variety of activities. For the outdoor enthusiast - enjoy all that Colorado has to offer with the Arkansas Head Waters only 15 miles away. In addition, the area affords opportunities to do do anything outdoors with the National Forest, Bureau of Land Management and State lands just a short commute away. Canon City and the Royal Gorge Area is only 25 miles from the property.
